        "    \"Synthesize a minimal {fw} program that probes the listed APIs for the described misbehavior.\",\n",
        "    \"Mutate or compose a short {fw} test seed exposing the numerical-reliability issue below.\",\n",
        "    \"Produce a deterministic, minimal {fw} snippet suitable as a fuzzing seed for the issue described.\",\n",
        "]\n",
